page.title: 05My Family Cont.
page.content: much this year because my uncle Max stuck his foot in the side of it and broke it,so we bought another one. Another sport of ours is{fishing}but I'm not too fussed on it.One day my mother caught a dog fish,but was so frightened of it my father had to put it in to the sea.Another fish that was caught was a conga-eel,but as it was trying to bite the dinghy my father had to cut the line. A successful catch was caught by my sister.The fish that was caught was a sea-trout which I called Henry. Henry was eaten for tea.
